                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">

                            <a href="/">
                                Home
                            </a>

                            <span>
                                >
                            </span>
                            <span>
                                Career
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <span class="section-label">career</span>
                    <h1>Build something <br class="d-lg-block d-none">
                        that
                        <span>endures.</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p>Join a team that believes in doing things the right way- thoughtfully <br
                            class="d-lg-block d-none"> engineered, responsibly
                        built, and designed to
                        last. <br class="d-lg-block d-none">
                        We are always looking for people who share our values.

                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
